02:12.870 --> 02:14.120
It could be anything.

02:14.240 --> 02:17.170
She's skittish,she's nervous,
she has a hard time focusing.

02:17.270 --> 02:19.420
It could be any one of your college pitfalls.

02:19.520 --> 02:21.700
It could be sex,drugs,guitar hero.

02:21.800 --> 02:24.290
So you want me to give her a job just in case she has a ghost?

02:24.450 --> 02:26.320
And if she doesn't,what do you want me to do then?

02:26.420 --> 02:27.730
Clean her dorm room,do her laundry?

02:27.920 --> 02:29.880
Melinda,this girl's father was my mentor.

02:29.950 --> 02:31.590
Please.I'm begging you.

02:32.210 --> 02:33.880
Hi!I'm sorry I'm late.

02:33.950 --> 02:34.500
You're not late.

02:34.590 --> 02:35.570
Late was 10 minutes ago.

02:35.730 --> 02:37.460
You're in a different time zone,kylie!

02:37.610 --> 02:40.890
I know,I know,I'm not sure what happened.

02:41.010 --> 02:42.820
I said informal job interview.

02:42.930 --> 02:44.360
I didn't mean that informal.

02:44.780 --> 02:45.540
Oh,well,moving right along.

02:45.560 --> 02:48.870
Kylie,melinda,melinda,kylie.

02:49.230 --> 02:49.850
Hi.

02:50.870 --> 02:53.900
It's just,it was really dark,
and I really thought that someone was.

02:55.290 --> 02:55.990
whatever.

02:56.420 --> 02:57.100
I'm sorry.

02:57.250 --> 02:59.850
You went out on a limb for me,
and I completely blew it.

03:00.300 --> 03:02.570
I guess the,uh,the job is history.

03:02.630 --> 03:03.680
No.No,not at all.

03:04.210 --> 03:05.190
When do you want to start?

03:05.960 --> 03:08.130
