24:26.370 --> 24:27.650
I'm with you, I think.

24:28.020 --> 24:29.770
The falling through the
glass, the heavy breathing,

24:29.790 --> 24:32.670
the things that he was
haunting kylie with,

24:32.690 --> 24:34.110
it's all things
from the movie,

24:34.130 --> 24:35.530
so it has to mean
something to her.

24:35.940 --> 24:37.170
Wait a minute, what was that?

24:37.320 --> 24:38.120
I didn't see that before.

24:38.150 --> 24:40.270
It's one of the soundtracks
attached to the raw footage.

24:40.290 --> 24:43.030
