-let's do one more.
-What?

24:46.230 --> 24:49.350
Well, that's toby, but you
can hear someone else. Listen.

24:49.390 --> 24:51.570
What? Why? We're not gonna
get a better take than that.

24:51.570 --> 24:53.040
-It's kylie.
-Yeah.

24:53.040 --> 24:54.680
She was working with him.

24:54.700 --> 24:57.020
Just not in front
of the camera.

25:17.840 --> 25:20.350
Hey, kylie, it's melinda.

25:20.360 --> 25:22.050
If you're there,
please pick up.

