Why don't you tell me exactly
what happened that night.

27:09.140 --> 27:11.160
I was supposed to be there.

27:12.610 --> 27:14.200
He had the shot all set up.

27:14.230 --> 27:16.100
It was actually pretty cool.

27:16.960 --> 27:20.210
This interior angle shot
of the priest falling.

27:20.630 --> 27:24.800
Bruce quit, so toby
had to stand in.

27:27.970 --> 27:29.610
It was a 2-person job.

27:32.240 --> 27:37.220
And I guess he
tripped, and fell.

27:42.320 --> 27:43.560
It's horrible.

27:44.410 --> 27:45.950
That's what happened to toby.

27:46.240 --> 27:47.450
But you weren't there.

27:49.050 --> 27:50.480
It was an accident, so.

27:51.330 --> 27:53.270
why do you think
it's your fault?

27:53.290 --> 27:54.550
Because.

27:55.440 --> 27:57.200
that's the day I
lost my scholarship.

27:59.800 --> 28:01.710
I've just been so invested
in making this movie

28:01.740 --> 28:03.930
