28:24.110 --> 28:26.380
Yes, you do, and
that's what scares you.

28:26.440 --> 28:29.280
I haven't even told my
friends about working with you.

28:38.120 --> 28:41.910
What embarrasses you
more, me or making movies?

28:44.150 --> 28:47.240
