29:22.510 --> 29:23.770
It's never about you.

29:24.350 --> 29:26.920
You think hiding behind
a camera gives you a pass.

29:27.260 --> 29:30.020
From our friendship and
from all human interaction.

29:30.050 --> 29:32.350
