walked away like that.

29:56.070 --> 29:57.460
I don't think
toby's haunting you

29:57.470 --> 29:59.140
because he thinks
you killed him.

29:59.170 --> 30:01.360
Of course he does, why
else would he be doing this?

30:01.380 --> 30:03.760
I think he wants you
to face your worst fear,

30:04.240 --> 30:06.490
whatever it is
about that movie.

30:07.520 --> 30:08.590
God.

30:09.920 --> 30:11.610
