30:11.640 --> 30:12.600
What do you mean?

30:12.620 --> 30:14.960
I know why the
exorcist scares me.

30:19.270 --> 30:24.300
The day my dad died, a priest
was reading his last rites.

30:25.590 --> 30:27.040
