what he wants, then.

30:42.320 --> 30:44.060
I want her to finish it.

30:45.700 --> 30:48.560
If she's faced her fears,
I want her to finish it.

30:48.580 --> 30:50.410
Finish what?

30:51.590 --> 30:52.920
Is he here?

30:55.560 --> 30:56.710
He was.

30:58.810 --> 31:00.030
What did he say?

31:00.580 --> 31:03.890
He said if you faced your
fears, he wants you to finish it.

31:04.240 --> 31:06.310
Do you know what that means?

31:06.330 --> 31:07.710
It means.

31:10.690 --> 31:12.250
he's not gonna stop.

31:13.230 --> 31:15.940
And this isn't gonna
end, and you can'T.

31:16.550 --> 31:17.310
help me.

31:17.310 --> 31:18.510
Yes, I can.

31:20.330 --> 31:21.540
I promise.

31:36.940 --> 31:39.490
You need to leave kylie alone.

31:40.470 --> 31:41.880
That's funny.

31:42.320 --> 31:43.810
