31:45.350 --> 31:47.360
She needs to figure it out on her own.

31:47.640 --> 31:50.680
Why is that important to you,
that she finishes the movie?

31:51.290 --> 31:53.180
Why do you this to people?

31:53.280 --> 31:56.190
Everyone has something that they're afraid of;

31:56.280 --> 31:57.910
something that holds them back.

31:57.920 --> 32:00.260
There's always a reason.

32:00.270 --> 32:02.610
Like you,and those slasher films.

32:02.620 --> 32:03.440
Let's look at that.

32:03.450 --> 32:04.750
Give me a break.

32:04.760 --> 32:10.140
Don't you ever wonder why those films
leave you feeling sick and exposed?

32:10.730 --> 32:13.170
What deep,dark memory do they stir?

32:13.180 --> 32:14.140
I don't need your help.

32:14.150 --> 32:17.110
Those films are usually about abandonment.

32:17.910 --> 32:19.280
Who abandoned you,melinda?

32:19.590 --> 32:21.680
Who left you alone in the dark?

32:22.750 --> 32:24.030
Your mother?

32:24.860 --> 32:26.020
Your father?

32:27.780 --> 32:29.230
That's it,isn't it?

32:30.600 --> 32:32.660
- Was he a
